00:40:37,840 --> 00:40:39,860
Sister, a latte.

662
00:40:43,480 --> 00:40:45,340
What happened to your head?

663
00:40:45,340 --> 00:40:47,399
I was filming for "Master, Hit Me Again."

664
00:40:47,399 --> 00:40:49,900
It's a bruise from my master.

665
00:40:49,900 --> 00:40:51,980
Nana-chan, can I take a photo with you?

666
00:40:51,980 --> 00:40:53,780
Sure.

667
00:41:01,240 --> 00:41:03,099
Your boyfriend is a great photographer.

668
00:41:03,100 --> 00:41:05,340
He outdid himself today.

669
00:41:05,340 --> 00:41:06,680
Nana-chan, I really love you.

670
00:41:06,680 --> 00:41:08,500
I like listening to you sing.

671
00:41:08,500 --> 00:41:10,439
- Thank you.
- I watched your live streams all the time.

672
00:41:10,439 --> 00:41:12,600
Thank you so much.

